&lt;Ione Inc>, which buys, sells andmanages retail gift, sundries and smokeshops located in hotels,said it successfully completed a 1.8 mln share common stockinitial public offering at 25 cts a share.    Rudy Steury, Ione president, said Ione will use theproceeds to further develop its retail shop network, as well asto purchase and resell more shops. Reuter&#3;